163
00:24:39,000 --> 00:24:43,000
Kazari, you go inside first.

164
00:25:18,000 --> 00:25:22,000
Suzuki-san.

165
00:25:42,000 --> 00:25:46,000
Mom, I'm sorry.

166
00:25:46,000 --> 00:25:50,000
