191
00:29:50,000 --> 00:29:54,000
And after that, someone beat me up too.

192
00:30:03,000 --> 00:30:07,000
Hey! Anyone there?!

193
00:30:07,000 --> 00:30:11,000
Open up!

194
00:30:13,000 --> 00:30:17,000
Cut it out!
You crying?

195
00:30:20,000 --> 00:30:24,000
