216
00:33:48,000 --> 00:33:51,000
Who locked us up in here?

217
00:33:51,000 --> 00:33:55,000
Don't know.
It seems they all were kidnapped.

218
00:33:57,000 --> 00:34:01,000
So you couldn't get into the
room beyond that one?

219
00:34:11,000 --> 00:34:14,000
Well then, this time try going this way.

220
00:34:14,000 --> 00:34:16,000
You go, sis!

221
00:34:16,000 --> 00:34:19,000
I can't go in there,
that's why I'm asking you!

222
00:34:19,000 --> 00:34:23,000
You're not asking me to,
you're ordering me to!

223
00:34:41,000 --> 00:34:43,000
I'm not evil!

224
00:34:43,000 --> 00:34:45,000
A college student?

225
00:34:45,000 --> 00:34:49,000
Yeah.
She said she was caught yesterday.

226
00:34:49,000 --> 00:34:53,000
They kidnap a woman every day?
That's insane.

227
00:34:54,000 --> 00:34:58,000
