253
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:38,000
You said you didn't need it, didn't you.

254
00:37:58,000 --> 00:38:02,000
- Sis, I want some too.
- You ate it all yourself yesterday, didn't you.

255
00:38:18,000 --> 00:38:22,000
You came back.

256
00:38:22,000 --> 00:38:24,000
