257
00:38:24,000 --> 00:38:28,000
Say... my older sister asked me to collect
everyone's personal belongings.

258
00:38:30,000 --> 00:38:35,000
By themselves they might be useless,
but if we put them together they might be of use.

259
00:38:40,000 --> 00:38:44,000
And it wouldn't just be for your own gain?

260
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:50,000
If we can save ourselves,
we'll save everyone, won't we!

261
00:38:51,000 --> 00:38:55,000
I wonder...

262
00:38:59,000 --> 00:39:03,000
Can something like this be of use?

263
00:39:06,000 --> 00:39:09,000
Too early for you yet, huh?

264
00:39:09,000 --> 00:39:11,000
What is this?

265
00:39:11,000 --> 00:39:15,000
How long have have you been here?

266
00:39:15,000 --> 00:39:17,000
